{"tid":2218199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人其實要成立自己的Virtual貨幣","createTime":"2020-09-26T05:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T05:03:09.000Z","uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e879619266236335bc81d15fd172a50e82f6a1b","tid":2218199,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"幾年前已經係高登提出要有自已世界公認的Virtual貨幣，用AI 同VR （eg. Web 3d, Unity3d) 去建立Virtual World，可以多一些Youtuber join, 同實體商店建立聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n利用Virtual world技術, 創造廣東話同英文交流區/經濟區, 鍵盤戰士可以在由居民組成的專門市場，同一些實體公司合作做網店或把虛擬財產兌換成美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.abload.de/img/hkship2012-08-1920-45y4qlf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abload.de%2Fimg%2Fhkship2012-08-1920-45y4qlf.jpg&h=c72a8ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可令更多外國人 係香港的虛擬世界學習 廣東話/生活。 <br />\n<br />\n再建一個Virtual香港，每人都有股份，選舉自己CEO。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wakeupandsmelltheashes.files.wordpress.com/2012/09/greenshot_2012-09-14_19-56-40.jpg?w%201280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwakeupandsmelltheashes.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F09%2Fgreenshot_2012-09-14_19-56-40.jpg%3Fw%25201280&h=494b445b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://soapandvideotapes.files.wordpress.com/2012/10/8b57093d5f559cc8d15dee5aff6d1ef2e866a417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoapandvideotapes.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F10%2F8b57093d5f559cc8d15dee5aff6d1ef2e866a417.jpg&h=762ad299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mzr0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fmzr0i.jpg&h=9d628f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zub5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fzub5c.jpg&h=8ae3a7db&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}